hopobject.body: How much will it cost to send this letter to ? walmart drug prices atorvastatin Memo to Rush Limbaugh: Sarah Palin's distaste for jerks who use 'retard' as an insult goes for right-wing pals like you, too. The ex-Alaska governor took the talkmeister to task in February after he waded into the firestorm over White House Chief of Staff Rahm Emanuel's use of the word 'retarded' - and promptly committed the same offense. 'Our political correct society is acting like some giant insult's taken place by calling a bunch of people who are retards, retards,' Limbaugh said on his show. 'I mean these people, these liberal activists are kooks.'
